OL,4,Cpistol to Myleene Klass to be sentenced
OL,6,FA man from Birmingham who was
OL,7,Fconvicted of stalking TV and radio
OL,8,Fstar Myleene Klass after sending her
OL,9,Fan air pistol, handcuffs, a police
OL,10,Funiform and "disturbing" letters will
OL,11,Fbe sentenced next week.
OL,13,FPeter Windsor, 61, who was also found
OL,14,Fguilty of stalking Klass's Classic FM
OL,15,Fcolleague Katie Breathwick by sending
OL,16,Fher details of a DIY will-writing kit
OL,17,Fand other "raving" and "unhinged"
OL,18,Fmail, will face a sentencing hearing
OL,19,Fat Warwick Crown Court on December
OL,20,F19th.
