OL,6,FA trial at Birmingham Crown Court in
OL,7,FOctober heard Windsor, of Stechford,
OL,8,Fleft Klass feeling "sheer terror"
OL,9,Fafter sending her the items.
OL,11,FWindsor, who has been diagnosed with
OL,12,Fschizophrenia and claimed he was not
OL,13,Fguilty by reason of insanity, denied
OL,14,Fstalking both Klass and Breathwick by
OL,15,Fsending items to Classic FM's central
OL,16,FLondon studios between March 2020 and
OL,17,FAugust 2024.
OL,19,FHowever, jurors reached unanimous
OL,20,Fguilty verdicts on October 7th after
OL,21,Ffour hours of deliberations.
